-- Greenlight Capital adds positions in Conn's, SunEdison
-- 
-- Tue Apr 22, 2014 02:38PM EDT
-- None



April 22 (Reuters) - Greenlight Capital's David Einhorn said in his latest letter to clients on Tuesday that the firm has shorted a group of momentum stocks the firm dubs 'the bubble basket.'

Greenlight also said the firm closed short positions in Chipotle Mexican Grill <CMG.N> and Michael Kors <KORS.N> in the first quarter while closing long positions in General Motors <GM.N>, Delphi Automotive <DLPH.N>, NCR Corp. <NCR.N> and DST Systems Inc. <DST.N> for the same period.